{"id":"gob","term":"Gob","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>A pit, a place mentioned in <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Samuel 21:18\">2 Sam. 21:18</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Samuel 21:19\">19</a>; called also Gezer, in <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 20:4\">1 Chr. 20:4</a>.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["2 Samuel 21:18","2 Samuel 21:19","1 Chronicles 20:4"]}